725218f-a.title: Queens: 32nd Avenue - Higgins Street
725218f-a.text:
32nd Avenue, north side, between Higgins and 132nd Streets,
viewing west toward the latter and showing three dwellings of
workmen of nearby industrial establishments. These appear on
maps as early as 18'3. 32nd Avenue was formerly Myrtle Avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 13, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
